Use the AVG aggregate function to find the average salary of employees in each department.

mysql> select dept_id,avg(emp_salary) as `average salary` from employee group by dept_id;
+---------+----------------+
| dept_id | average salary |
+---------+----------------+
|       1 |   52500.000000 |
|       3 |   40000.000000 |
+---------+----------------+
2 rows in set (0.00 sec)